# .dockerignore — Files excluded from the Docker build context

# Dependencies (installed inside the image)
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log

# Development files
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/dist/
**/build/

# Editor & OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/Thumbs.db

# Git
**/.git
**/.gitignore

# Docs (not needed at runtime)
docs/
wiki/
*.md

# Test files
**/__tests__/
**/*.test.js
**/*.spec.js
